videos.description: Donald Trump and Elon Musk watched Starship launch, gazing together as it rocketed to space.

This is the moment a woman screamed in a little girls face at a Kamala Harris rally. The Democrat woman, who is yet to be identified, started screaming in the child's face and was then pulled away by another attendee. She was heard saying: 'I don't give a f**, your dad's a b**.' The man had already been surrounded by unhappy Harris supporters and 'Boos' were heard before the woman began yelling. He picked the child up and speaks into his microphone saying: 'Are you ashamed at all? Are you ashamed?' To which she responded 'No'.  #democrat #rally #kamalaharris #child #girl #republican #scary
